headline: Johnson Controls International (JCI) Reports Mixed Earnings Results With US$310 Million Buyback Completion
summary: Johnson Controls International (JCI) recently reported a revenue increase to $6,052 million for Q3 2025, though net income fell to $701 million from the previous year. An anticipated organic sales growth and an active share buyback program, with 3.8 million shares repurchased, contributed to a 23% price increase over the last quarter.
